><Case(1)>\r\nSpawns in: <Value>IntegerParameter(3)</Value>:<TwoDigitValue>IntegerParameter(4)</TwoDigitValue></Case><Case(2)>\r\nHP: <Value>IntegerParameter(5)</Value>%</Case><Case(3)></Case></Switch> "]},"12800":{"Text":["Clear <Sheet(PlaceName,IntegerParameter(1),0)/>","Clear <SheetEn(PlaceName,2,IntegerParameter(1),2,1)/>"]},"15002":{"Text":["Defeat Bronze Bull","Defeat the Bronze Bull"]},"15010":{"Text":["In the next match, <Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight> and Bronze Bull will fight for a place in the Thal group final!","In the next match, <Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight> and the Bronze Bull will fight for a place in the Thal group final!"]},"15013":{"Text":["And <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/> stops Bronze Bull's furious charge!","And <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/> stops the Bronze Bull's furious charge!"]},"40200":{"Text":["Defeat Brute Bomber","Defeat the Brute Bomber"]},"40713":{"Text":["","That struck square!"]},"40714":{"Text":["","Oof! Will the challenger be alright!?"]},"40715":{"Text":["","Oh no, they couldn't avoid that one!"]},"40716":{"Text":["","That must have hurt! But they're not out of the fight yet!"]},"40717":{"Text":["","Effortlessly dodged!"]},"40718":{"Text":["","Amazing! They clearly anticipated that attack!"]},"40719":{"Text":["","A stylish evasion, well done!"]},"40720":{"Text":["","Avoided with ease! They knew just what to do!"]},"40721":{"Text":["","Oh no, that was too much for the challenger!"]},"40722":{"Text":["","The challenger's down! Is this the end!?"]},"40723":{"Text":["","The challenger rises again! Can they turn this around!?"]},"40724":{"Text":["","They're back on their feet! Let's see if they can stay standing!"]},"41709":{"Text":["_rsv_41709_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Death is but a prelude to nothingness..."]},"41710":{"Text":["_rsv_41710_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Winds of Darkness, usher all unto oblivion!"]},"41711":{"Text":["_rsv_41711_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Death abide in my breast!"]},"41712":{"Text":["_rsv_41712_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Wind abide in my breast!"]},"41807":{"Text":["_rsv_41807_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","I told you it would make a great necklace."]},"41808":{"Text":["_rsv_41808_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Ohhh...it's beautiful! I think it'll really suit you!"]},"41809":{"Text":["_rsv_41809_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Me? But I thought you should have it..."]},"41810":{"Text":["_rsv_41810_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Is this ice? Where did this come from?"]},"41816":{"Text":["_rsv_41816_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Still you resist. Then we shall unleash the Light within!"]},"41817":{"Text":["_rsv_41817_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","No! I won't let you!"]},"41823":{"Text":["_rsv_41823_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Ryne, are you alright!?"]},"41824":{"Text":["_rsv_41824_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","I am thanks to you, Gaia."]},"41825":{"Text":["_rsv_41825_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","You're Mitron! Ugh... Aaaaaahhh!"]},"41828":{"Text":["_rsv_41828_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Her awakening is incomplete... Their memories weaken the link."]},"41829":{"Text":["_rsv_41829_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Such impediments to our resonance must be expunged."]},"41830":{"Text":["_rsv_41830_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","The time is come. Together, we shall rejoin the Darkness!"]},"41831":{"Text":["_rsv_41831_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","We shall bring eternal harmony."]},"41832":{"Text":["_rsv_41832_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Tranquility and vitality in perfect balance..."]},"41833":{"Text":["_rsv_41833_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","No one will erase our promise. No one!"]},"41834":{"Text":["_rsv_41834_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","This cacophony... My head..."]},"41835":{"Text":["_rsv_41835_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","So close to realizing our perfect utopia..."]},"41836":{"Text":["_rsv_41836_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","I'll never stop. As many times as it takes!"]},"41837":{"Text":["_rsv_41837_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","When next I return, I <Emphasis>will</Emphasis> succeed!"]},"41838":{"Text":["_rsv_41838_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Begone from my memories! Every last trace of you!"]},"41839":{"Text":["_rsv_41839_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","We're not going to disappear!"]},"41840":{"Text":["_rsv_41840_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Aye, we're too stubborn for that!"]},"41841":{"Text":["_rsv_41841_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","We'll get through this, Ryne!"]},"41842":{"Text":["_rsv_41842_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Yes, together!"]},"41843":{"Text":["_rsv_41843_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Our friend won't fail us!"]},"41844":{"Text":["_rsv_41844_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","You'd better not, or I'll never let you hear the end of it!"]},"41845":{"Text":["_rsv_41845_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","We won't give up on the future!"]},"41846":{"Text":["_rsv_41846_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Please, let our prayers be heard!"]},"41847":{"Text":["_rsv_41847_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","If this place cannot be our utopia..."]},"41848":{"Text":["_rsv_41848_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Then naught in existence holds meaning!"]},"41849":{"Text":["_rsv_41849_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","That's a little melodramatic, don't you think!?"]},"41850":{"Text":["_rsv_41850_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","You can weather this! I know you can!"]},"41851":{"Text":["_rsv_41851_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Yaaaaaargh!"]},"41852":{"Text":["_rsv_41852_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Our promise fades..."]},"41853":{"Text":["_rsv_41853_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Light and Darkness, gather to me!"]},"41854":{"Text":["_rsv_41854_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","You endure? Another approach, then..."]},"41855":{"Text":["_rsv_41855_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","I am yours, and you are mine!"]},"41856":{"Text":["_rsv_41856_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","What is this!?"]},"41857":{"Text":["_rsv_41857_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","I won't let you do as you please!"]},"41858":{"Text":["_rsv_41858_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","What is this!?"]},"41859":{"Text":["_rsv_41859_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Ryne... Are you there?"]},"41860":{"Text":["_rsv_41860_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Gaia?"]},"41861":{"Text":["_rsv_41861_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61","Raaaaaargggh!"]},"41900":{"Text":["","Let's begin, shall we?"]},"41901":{"Text":["","Can the challenger defeat the wolf in his own lair!?"]},"41902":{"Text":["","I wonder if you can keep up..."]},"41903":{"Text":["","Such speed\u2500it's as if there's a pack of him!"]},"41904":{"Text":["","Can you fend off a pack of wolves?"]},"41905":{"Text":["","I do like toying with my prey."]},"41906":{"Text":["","Fenrir's power can be wielded in surprising ways."]},"41907":{"Text":["","Where did that colossal thing come from!?"]},"41908":{"Text":["","He's put the colossus to the sword!"]},"41909":{"Text":["","Not bad, not bad. But we've scarcely begun."]},"41910":{"Text":["","Bear my biting winds!"]},"41911":{"Text":["","Still you stand... How delightful!"]},"41912":{"Text":["","_rsv_41912_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41913":{"Text":["","_rsv_41913_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41914":{"Text":["","_rsv_41914_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41915":{"Text":["","_rsv_41915_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41916":{"Text":["","_rsv_41916_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41917":{"Text":["","_rsv_41917_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41918":{"Text":["","_rsv_41918_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41919":{"Text":["","_rsv_41919_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41920":{"Text":["","_rsv_41920_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41921":{"Text":["","_rsv_41921_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41922":{"Text":["","_rsv_41922_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41923":{"Text":["","_rsv_41923_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41924":{"Text":["","_rsv_41924_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41925":{"Text":["","_rsv_41925_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41926":{"Text":["","_rsv_41926_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41927":{"Text":["","_rsv_41927_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41928":{"Text":["","_rsv_41928_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41929":{"Text":["","_rsv_41929_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41930":{"Text":["","_rsv_41930_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41931":{"Text":["","_rsv_41931_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41932":{"Text":["","_rsv_41932_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41933":{"Text":["","Defeat the Howling Blade"]},"41934":{"Text":["","_rsv_41934_-1_1_0_0_S13095D61_E13095D61"]},"41935":{"Text":["","Have at you!"]}}}